These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, turquise, fuchsia, mauve, emerald
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, puzzles, baking, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes grey is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Color   | turquise | fuchsia | grey | emerald | mauve |
| Hobby   | card-games    | drawing | puzzles     | baking       | magic-tricks  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, dunhill, old-henry, aristoff, alhambra
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, lawyer, doctor, photographer, project-manager
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is in the middle##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is the doctor##1
6. the project-manager is the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the photographer is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Cigar      | dunhill | old-henry | bolivar | aristoff | alhambra |
| Job   | doctor  | photographer   | nurse       | lawyer    | project-manager   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, whist, canasta, poker
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, american, canadian, colombian, british
1. the american is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the british##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
5. the british is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Game        | whist | canasta | mah-jongg | backgammon | poker |
| Nationality   | american  | chinese      | british | canadian | colombian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, august, july, september, april
City: venice, hamburg, rome, edinburgh, nizza
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday   | september    | january        | july | august | april |
| City     | venice | edinburgh | nizza  | hamburg   | rome |

