.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, roller, skateboard, motorbike
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bluemaster, alhambra, davidoff, swisher
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Transport    | roller   | scooter     | snowmobile   | skateboard         | motorbike |
| Cigar   | chaman | davidoff | alhambra | swisher | bluemaster     |

