.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
House: tower, farmhouse, gothic-revival, futuristic, colonial
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, cola, 7up, water
1. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking cola is the gothic-revival house##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| House       | futuristic   | gothic-revival   | farmhouse | colonial | tower |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola | 7up   | water | mirinda       |

