.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, scientific, documentary, martial-arts
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, dahlia, orchid, iris
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growszinnia is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Movie-Genre     | satire   | scientific  | martial-arts      | mystery | documentary     |
| Flower   | orchid | dahlia | poppy | zinnia   | iris |

