2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Transport     | bus | subway       | skateboard | scooter | taxi    |
| Flower   | bellflower   | daisy | daffodil  | zinnia     | marigold |

