.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, weightlifting, badminton, snowboarding
House: victorian, cape-cod, palace, futuristic, colonial
1. the palace house is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
5. the colonial house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the cape-cod house##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Sport         | badminton | rowing | weightlifting | snowboarding | water-polo |
| House   | palace       | futuristic   | colonial         | cape-cod   | victorian   |

