4. the coach is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
