.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, ivory, fuchsia, ebony, green
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, march, february, august, september
1. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes green is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Color   | fuchsia | red      | ebony | ivory | green |
| Birthday     | august  | march | january     | september     | february  |

