.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, lilac, blood-red, grey, chestnut
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, crime, spy, satire, drama
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Color           | grey     | chestnut | white | blood-red  | lilac |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | drama               | crime     | spy | satire |

