.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, coral, apricot, brown, amber
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, poppy, bellflower, sunflower, orchid
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
7. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Color   | amber     | apricot       | lilac     | coral  | brown  |
| Flower      | sunflower | aconite | poppy | orchid | bellflower |

