.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, mirinda, water, tea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, baseball, snowboarding, cycling, swimming
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea | mirinda | coffee | water |
| Sport           | swimming | cycling  | baseball    | weightlifting  | snowboarding   |

 